397
00:27:53.418 --> 00:27:55.886
- Dank je.
- Graag gedaan.

398
00:27:56.121 --> 00:27:57.588
- Alsjeblieft.
- Dank je.

399
00:27:57.823 --> 00:27:59.290
Graag gedaan.

400
00:28:07.966 --> 00:28:10.434
- Mr. Schneebly?
- Ja?

401
